    controls:["Security awareness training specific to OT staff","Email filtering with sandboxing","MFA for all remote and privileged OT access","Phishing-resistant MFA (FIDO2) for critical systems","Separate email domain for OT engineering staff","Inbound attachment blocking for OT jump servers","Simulated phishing exercises for OT personnel"],
